  "description": "This dish is a play on the classic breakfast dish 'kedgeree' â€“ a rice dish of smoked fish and boiled eggs. This veggie version uses arborio rice, saffron and curry spices and topped with roasted cherry tomatoes, cashews, fresh coriander and lemon. (Naturally gluten-free, but unsuitable for coeliacs).",
